<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Restablecer contraseña</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .card {
          width: 90% !important;
          padding: 20px !important;
        }
        .title {
          font-size: 20px !important;
        }
        .text {
          font-size: 14px !important;
          text-align: center !important;
        }
        .btn {
          padding: 10px 18px !important;
          font-size: 14px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0; padding:0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"
      style="background: url('https://picsum.photos/800/600?blur') no-repeat center center; background-size: cover; padding: 40px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table class="card" width="500" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
            style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); max-width: 500px; width: 100%;">
            <tr>
              <td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
                <h2 class="title"
                  style="margin:0; font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Hola <strong>{{fullname}}</strong></h2>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text"
                style="padding: 15px 0; font-size: 16px; color:#444; line-height:1.5;">
                Haga clic en el siguiente botón para restablecer su contraseña:
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                <a href="{{resetLink}}"
                  class="btn"
                  style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
                          color: #fff;
                          text-decoration: none;
                          padding: 12px 24px;
                          border-radius: 8px;
                          font-weight: bold;
                          display: inline-block;">
                  Restablecer contraseña
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style="padding-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color:#666; text-align:center;">
                Si usted no solicitó este cambio, puede ignorar este correo.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
